echo -e "${CYAN}━━━ SUPPORTED COINS ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━${NC}"
echo -e "    ${GREEN}SHA-256d${NC}: BTC  BCH  BC2  DGB       ${GREEN}Scrypt${NC}: LTC  DOGE  DGB-S  PEP  CAT"
echo -e "    ${GREEN}AuxPoW${NC}:  BTC+NMC  BTC+FBTC  BTC+SYS  BTC+XMY  LTC+DOGE  LTC+PEP"
